overview: Today, the young couple, Ilham and Rina, are traveling in search of a new home. They were attracted by the house that was guarded by Mrs. Ratri. But behind the beauty that this house offers, there is a dark history of the past that continues to haunt you. Odd events emerged. Terrorizing Ilham, Rina and Ratri. Will the bloody history in this house repeat itself?
title: Bisikan 69
